ockquote>人愈大一個一個本來交心既朋友都離自己而去<br />\n都係自己一個算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但有時有啲嘢係要keep 你唔搵人人地唔搵你 段友情就會無啦啦無咗<br />\n試下搵返啲朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d04d183a87fdb5cd42b63ea3d5785e6e98d2162","tid":47943,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>特登去識反而會識唔到既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇特登去識<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 突然感觸所以出post講下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緣份既野話唔埋既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df70a6b48c745b9ab82a73c8b805f07e6a7a7a23","tid":47943,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我朋友都唔多 但真心朋友仲叫有<br />\n但有時都想擴大社交圈子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你點識到佢地，交心既程度係點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全部都係中學 大學同學<br />\n咩都講 分手淨係會同佢地講 定期會出嚟食飯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想要你講個種朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450c51c9ba24c2b12e06f08c7a3fd0745ff4f789","tid":47943,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:41:09.000Z","msg":"質性自然，非矯厲所得。<br />\n以心待人，保留自己個性，自然有知已<br />\n我去旅行嗰陣，識過其他國家嘅人，仲有keep in touch乜都講"},{"pid":"fc1e24b42c8fb259f17b89a4fe8c715a16e51244","tid":47943,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交心得一、兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係唔會成日見到<br />\n我本身比較毒 難識人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都好呀，唔洗成日見，一有事一定仆出黎既幫你先係真兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29175f7aacc6d3fa0a8882547001b16c8c836569","tid":47943,"uid":1952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背後冷冷的一刀 最令人刻骨銘心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾年前我都有過呢種感受<br />\n但幾年過去 個個朋友突然搵返我 話想同我做朋友 其實我都已經無咩嘢 我聽日仲約咗佢見面食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd624b753dd5ccf9962d6f343c86051332543eb","tid":47943,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>質性自然，非矯厲所得。<br />\n以心待人，保留自己個性，自然有知已<br />\n我去旅行嗰陣，識過其他國家嘅人，仲有keep in touch乜都講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似明明地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做番自己就可以嗎？anyway 多謝你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a1f4fca355fefd88ef346fa7883f17c54d07e8","tid":47943,"uid":1952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你點識到佢地，交心既程度係點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全部都係中學 大學同學<br />\n咩都講 分手淨係會同佢地講 定期會出嚟食飯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想要你講個種朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 佢地係我最重視嘅朋友 得閒無事whatspp 9up 不知幾開心<br />\n聖誕我地幾個仲約出嚟一齊取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d091ba590d86d3843f325673787cc04e36dec8","tid":47943,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背後冷冷的一刀 最令人刻骨銘心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相信世界仲有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d574e16d516e773fc0b7bcaf16331fcdcc052d0","tid":47943,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我自己都有問題，戒心好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會輕易講出真感受</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前試過相信朋友然後被背叛過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比ex背叛過，同埋見到老豆比識左30年既兄弟騙曬d$<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOh.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過見你上面講身邊朋友style喜好同你咁唔同，或者只係未遇到投契/夾既fd姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做朋友，有時亦真係要發掘下先會知可能有另一面係同你出奇地夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試過同同學識左兩年一d都唔熟，無端端R水吹話不如去行山，就真係去左行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係兩個人行山時傾左好多唔同野兼深入交流，就意外地成為左交心既fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔同環境下，同一個人可以同你擦出既火花都唔同，真係唔試過唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下用你既好奇心認識深入多d/廣d朋友，然後又試下逐d逐d咁分享下自己既野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時對方願唔願意回應你既用心，你會feel到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146d66024c64342db8b2a4fe983cbfa5305281d1","tid":47943,"uid":22312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>背後冷冷的一刀 最令人刻骨銘心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相信世界仲有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都信架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a4bdd688af818f66662c3066649b139e1256a3","tid":47943,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97bd6e8a1de1af1f3507fe5dba706e9128fdb60","tid":47943,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>質性自然，非矯厲所得。<br />\n以心待人，保留自己個性，自然有知已<br />\n我去旅行嗰陣，識過其他國家嘅人，仲有keep in touch乜都講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似明明地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做番自己就可以嗎？anyway 多謝你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做返自己之餘，仲要培養良好價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n我曾經同朋友飲酒講過，香港地金錢掛帥令唔少人都係利益主義者，好難達到外國果種重視人文嘅價值觀，利益真係凌駕關係？<br />\n<br />\n自問對利益呢樣嘢唔係太敏感，乜都以友誼為先，搞到自己有時諗埋一邊，覺得好奇怪，明明呢個社會嘅人好多都唔會咁諗。<br />\n<br />\n後來堅守自我，係因為違背唔到自己，而朋友都feel到嗰種真實感，就放心為友喇。結果有一次又飲酒，佢同我講，上次我講嘅野啟發到佢，佢反思過做人係咪真係以利益嚟衡量關係，所以佢就變到好以誠相待喇。後尾聽返佢啲朋友講，佢以前同我識嘅佢係兩個人嚟。<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係，做返你自己，諗下對關係嘅睇法，有心同你做friend嘅自然會嚟，而冇心嘅都可能畀你影響到，變得真心。自己都唔洗成日去諗有冇朋友，做好自己就無愧"},{"pid":"1339690cd3249bd477871e72c8a87b5d5403fcf2","tid":47943,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>背後冷冷的一刀 最令人刻骨銘心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相信世界仲有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都信架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過果種滋味 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78297bd2d4c2984c6e7fae84f986346405ae908","tid":47943,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前試過相信朋友然後被背叛過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比ex背叛過，同埋見到老豆比識左30年既兄弟騙曬d$<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOh.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過見你上面講身邊朋友style喜好同你咁唔同，或者只係未遇到投契/夾既fd姐<img src=\"/assets/faces